{\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here is everything you need to know.\", \"from\": 431, \"to\": 467, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 449}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are a number of reasons why runners may choose to wear sleeves, ranging from warmth to protection and safety.\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 487}, {\"ngram\": \"reasons\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 498}, {\"ngram\": \"runners\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 510}, {\"ngram\": \"sleeves\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 537}, {\"ngram\": \"warmth\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 558}, {\"ngram\": \"protection\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 572}, {\"ngram\": \"safety\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Arm sleeves are primarily worn for the compression benefit that they provide.\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Arm sleeves\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 597}, {\"ngram\": \"the compression benefit\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 644}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Compression sleeves can help reduce swelling induced by longer runs caused by muscle vibrations and tears, which induce an inflammatory response.\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 810, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Compression sleeves\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 684}, {\"ngram\": \"longer runs\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 732}, {\"ngram\": \"muscle vibrations\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 760}, {\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 770}, {\"ngram\": \"an inflammatory response\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 809}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This draws excess fluid into the arms and wearing compression arm sleeves can help prevent the swelling this can cause.\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 931, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"excess fluid\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"the arms\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"compression arm sleeves\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 885}, {\"ngram\": \"the swelling\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 915}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They can also be used as a recovery tool post-race by increasing the blood flow to the arms to reduce the chance of injury.\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 1056, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a recovery tool post\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"race\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 983}, {\"ngram\": \"the blood flow\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1012}, {\"ngram\": \"the arms\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1024}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"injury\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The running arm sleeves can keep your arms nice and warm, while also offering protection from the wind.\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1161, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The running arm sleeves\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1081}, {\"ngram\": \"your arms\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1100}, {\"ngram\": \"protection\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1146}, {\"ngram\": \"the wind\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Likewise, it can offer a layer of protection from the sun, although any runners should also make sure to apply sun protection to protect themselves from being out in UV rays for a long period of time.\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1363, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a layer\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1193}, {\"ngram\": \"protection\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1207}, {\"ngram\": \"the sun\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1220}, {\"ngram\": \"any runners\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"sun protection\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1288}, {\"ngram\": \"UV rays\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1336}, {\"ngram\": \"a long period\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1354}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many arm sleeves feature reflective detailing on them, meaning that they can help make runners who run 